        ]
      },
      "description": {
        "localized_texts": [
          {
            "language_code": "en",
            "text": "Wetland Studios Putrajaya is a one-of-a-kind edutainment indoor theme park not to be missed when you visit Putrajaya, Malaysia. Have fun learning about the past, present and how we can shape a better future as future generations to come.KRU Studios Sdn Bhd (KRU) is a multi-award-winning media and entertainment company in Malaysia, and an emerging brand globally.On 5 October 2022, Putrajaya Corporation and KRU signed a collaboration agreement whereby KRU is entrusted to design, market and operate Wetland Studios Putrajaya with the objective to promote the flora and fauna of Putrajaya Wetland Park using modern technology to create an immersive, memorable, entertaining, and rewarding experience for our visitors."
          }
        ]
      },
