            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Terms & Conditions: Admission Ticket is valid only on the selected visit date. In the event of technical malfunction and/or safety concerns, management reserves the right to suspend entry to exhibitions and reschedule, change, or cancel entry times or dates.Eligibility Adults are individuals aged 13 to 64 years old. Senior citizens are individuals aged 65 years old and above. Children are individuals aged 4 to 12 years old. At the point of entry, visitors may be required to present valid personal identification documents (e.g., MyKad, MyTentera, MyKid for Malaysians and/or Passport, MyPR, MyKAS for foreigners) for verification purposes.Attraction Access Customers are not permitted to bring animals into the venue.Additional Information Wear comfortable shoes suitable for walking. Bring insect repellent, especially during dusk and dawn. Stay hydrated by bringing your own water bottle.Important Notes The operator is not responsible for any loss, damage, death, or injury caused by patrons’ actions or negligence."
